{"tid":1009113,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"火牛有事？","createTime":"2019-02-05T03:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T23:13:44.000Z","uid":180705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d6073e8ee42b5a82966dfb95b8be4045c0151e","tid":1009113,"uid":180705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"唔知係唔係壞火牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早幾日幫部電腦加左顯示卡同埋SSD。 <br />\n之後每一次開機個陣,電腦會通電大概一秒左右(CPU風扇會轉一下,Mon冇畫面) 。<br />\n一秒後會自己斷電?(機箱既燈,MB同後邊LAN線既燈會熄左)，之後等一到兩秒到會自己通電(所有燈著返晒),正常進入WINDOWS。<br />\n唔知發生左咩事，請巴打幫手睇睇...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電腦配置:<br />\nGigabyte B150M-D3H MB<br />\nKINGSTON 16GB DDR4<br />\nI5-6500<br />\nANTEC TRUE POWER 550W 80PLUS GOLD<br />\n2 隻 1TB HD<br />\n<br />\n後加配置:<br />\nwd nvme 500gb<br />\nEVGA RTX 2060 XC ULTRA<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f065105005012fc0852f66647ba54c4a857eeb","tid":1009113,"uid":54777,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:44:34.000Z","msg":"唔似係壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似係唔夠電"},{"pid":"80bf0301c9239ccb7554cb25a5d6bdce30dda868","tid":1009113,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n550w"},{"pid":"576e1ca0c5b16833ce47307c0d33f6039e252d91","tid":1009113,"uid":707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"我有時都會咁，就咁睇應該夠電<br />\n粒cpu用得幾十w vga 頂多咪3百"},{"pid":"0